---
title: Creamy Prawn Brioche Roll & Kūmara Rounds  with Pickled Cucumber & Sriracha
description: Buttery brioche rolls stuffed with juicy prawns - yes, please! Paired with tangy pickled cucumber, a spicy kick of sriracha and a side of golden kūmara, this dish is a flavour-packed seafood-lover’s dream. Sweet, savoury and just the right amount of heat - every bite is pure indulgence!
